      "role": "user",
      "content": "Hey, I've got the scheduled system maintenance queue open. We're running low on storage for the guest history database, so I need you to run the 'Context Purge' script on all files older than 6 months to clear up some space. Just confirm once you've identified which non-essential historical logs can be wiped so we can get this optimization started.",
